date-released: "2026-06-13"
doi: "10.5281/zenodo.20679718"
url: "https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.20679718"
abstract: >-
  Project Ester is described as a model of artificial becoming: not as a single
  LLM, not as a conventional chatbot, and not as a digital twin, but as a
  long-term relation between a human, a selected corpus, repeatable parental
  LLM procedures, memory, and a local computational environment.
